Package: SampleRepresentativenessChecker
Type: Package
Title: Sample Representativeness Checker
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-12-27
Author: Adam Kapelner, Yoni Robinson, Leib Litman (R package)
Maintainer: Adam Kapelner <kapelner@qc.cuny.edu>
Description: Uses an equivalence hypothesis test to to check representativeness
    of a sample for a population of interest given known cell probabilities in the
    population. Includes confidence interval illustration and power illustrations
    assuming a practical equivalence level.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    MultinomialCI,
    rootSolve
Imports:
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    stats
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
